              <span>Hours of manual tracking</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="how-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">How It Works</span>
        <h2>Get Started in Minutes</h2>
        <p>No complicated setup. No training required.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Create Your Buckets</h3>
          <p>Organize members by department, location, or any grouping that fits your union structure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Add Your Members</h3>
          <p>Enter member details including contact info and mailing addresses for those without email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Upload Documents</h3>
          <p>When members submit signed paperwork, upload the PDF and they're marked in good standing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3>Export Reports</h3>
          <p>Generate Excel reports anytime. Perfect for headquarters or internal records.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
        <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is there a limit on members?</h3>
          <p>No. Add as many members as your local needs. Whether you have 50 or 5,000 members, the price is the same.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How many people can access the system?</h3>
          <p>Create unlimited admin accounts. Presidents get full control while Recording Secretaries handle data entry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What happens after the free trial?</h3>
          <p>After 30 days, you'll be asked to subscribe to continue. Your data is preserved during the trial.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is my data secure?</h3>
          <p>Yes. We use industry-standard encryption and secure cloud storage. Your member data is protected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I export my data?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. Export member lists to Excel anytime. Your data belongs to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you offer support?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Email support is included. We're here to help you get the most out of MIGS List.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Modernize Your Member Tracking?</h2>
        <p>Join union locals across Canada who trust MIGS List. Start your free trial today.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Start 30-Day Free Trial</a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">No credit card required. Cancel anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="pricing-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
      <p>&copy; 2024 MIGS List. Built for union locals across Canada.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

